WEBVTT

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:02.470
Good morning, family. I am excited to

00:00:02.480 --> 00:00:04.590
be with you all again today. I have a word

00:00:04.600 --> 00:00:07.309
for you. I was praying and

00:00:07.319 --> 00:00:09.430
seeking the Lord one night, and about 3:00

00:00:09.430 --> 00:00:09.440
AM,

00:00:09.440 --> 00:00:12.509
the Lord came to me

00:00:12.519 --> 00:00:14.470
very loudly in my spirit and

00:00:14.480 --> 00:00:16.670
said, 'Brandon, you are asking Me

00:00:16.680 --> 00:00:19.950
about who the

00:00:19.960 --> 00:00:23.269
major leaders in the End Time Army will

00:00:23.269 --> 00:00:23.279
be.'As

00:00:23.279 --> 00:00:25.550
I was praying about this, He

00:00:25.560 --> 00:00:27.950
said, 'John Kilpatrick will be one of the

00:00:27.960 --> 00:00:30.630
major voices in the End Time Army that you

00:00:30.640 --> 00:00:32.870
can trust and listen

00:00:32.870 --> 00:00:32.880
to.'This

00:00:32.880 --> 00:00:35.549
was what the Lord spoke to me, so I

00:00:35.559 --> 00:00:38.590
check in on his ministry every once in a

00:00:38.600 --> 00:00:40.950
while and listen to see what is going

00:00:40.960 --> 00:00:45.150
on. One of my family members sent

00:00:45.160 --> 00:00:49.670
me a video that he did a couple of Sundays

00:00:49.680 --> 00:00:52.830
ago about a word that the Lord gave

00:00:52.840 --> 00:00:55.549
him in the middle of the night. I

00:00:55.549 --> 00:00:55.559
am

00:00:55.559 --> 00:00:57.270
putting it all on

00:00:57.280 --> 00:00:59.150
here to show you that

00:00:59.160 --> 00:01:01.750
the Lord gave him a warning,

00:01:01.760 --> 00:01:05.189
telling him about major

00:01:05.199 --> 00:01:08.429
earthquakes and volcanoes

00:01:08.439 --> 00:01:09.870
that were going to start to

00:01:09.880 --> 00:01:12.590
take place. I believe what he was

00:01:12.600 --> 00:01:15.390
seeing was for the United States. I

00:01:15.390 --> 00:01:15.400
am

00:01:15.400 --> 00:01:18.870
telling you all, I saw a major event

00:01:18.880 --> 00:01:21.149
taking place; as he pointed out,

00:01:21.159 --> 00:01:22.789
what the Lord showed him is

00:01:22.799 --> 00:01:25.350
in Oregon. I do not want to go

00:01:25.350 --> 00:01:25.360
on

00:01:25.360 --> 00:01:27.350
until you can watch it.

00:01:27.350 --> 00:01:27.360
I

00:01:27.360 --> 00:01:30.830
want to tell you all this: it

00:01:30.830 --> 00:01:30.840
is

00:01:30.840 --> 00:01:34.270
amazing to see when God speaks to people

00:01:34.270 --> 00:01:34.280
who

00:01:34.280 --> 00:01:37.190
are prophetic. It

00:01:37.190 --> 00:01:37.200
is

00:01:37.200 --> 00:01:40.550
like a mirror; it

00:01:40.550 --> 00:01:40.560
is

00:01:40.560 --> 00:01:43.910
different, but it is the same because it

00:01:43.910 --> 00:01:43.920
is

00:01:43.920 --> 00:01:46.230
the same Spirit of the Lord. He

00:01:46.240 --> 00:01:48.670
speaks to each one of us differently

00:01:48.670 --> 00:01:48.680
in

00:01:48.680 --> 00:01:50.870
the way we interpret it, and

00:01:50.870 --> 00:01:50.880
I

00:01:50.880 --> 00:01:53.069
think it is amazing. I

00:01:53.079 --> 00:01:55.149
want to encourage you all to watch

00:01:55.159 --> 00:01:57.830
this whole thing. This is a prophetic

00:01:57.840 --> 00:02:01.389
message for today—a warning

00:02:01.399 --> 00:02:04.749
for what is coming. A major shift and a major

00:02:04.759 --> 00:02:07.029
shaking are about to take place in this

00:02:07.039 --> 00:02:09.669
world, and it is not just about America; it

00:02:09.669 --> 00:02:09.679
is

00:02:09.679 --> 00:02:13.390
about a worldwide wake-up. Jesus

00:02:13.400 --> 00:02:16.869
Christ is coming, and you better be ready.

00:02:16.879 --> 00:02:19.470
If you are not saved, today is your day.

00:02:19.480 --> 00:02:22.630
You need to get born again, turn,

00:02:22.640 --> 00:02:25.949
and repent of your sins, for Jesus Christ

00:02:25.959 --> 00:02:27.990
is coming. I want to encourage you all

00:02:27.990 --> 00:02:28.000
to

00:02:28.000 --> 00:02:30.470
please watch this

00:02:30.480 --> 00:02:34.030
whole thing; it will bless you. This

00:02:34.040 --> 00:02:37.990
sermon is amazing, and I hope

00:02:37.990 --> 00:02:38.000
it

00:02:38.000 --> 00:02:40.149
blesses you. Knowing this first:

00:02:40.159 --> 00:02:41.869
there shall come in the last days

00:02:41.879 --> 00:02:45.229
scoffers, walking after their own lusts

00:02:45.229 --> 00:02:45.239
and

00:02:45.239 --> 00:02:48.309
saying, 'Where is

00:02:48.319 --> 00:02:50.110
the promise of His

00:02:50.120 --> 00:02:52.750
coming? For since the fathers fell

00:02:52.750 --> 00:02:52.760
asleep—the

00:02:52.760 --> 00:02:54.630
ones who used to be alive

00:02:54.630 --> 00:02:54.640
and

00:02:54.640 --> 00:02:57.390
told us the Lord was

00:02:57.390 --> 00:02:57.400
coming—He

00:02:57.400 --> 00:03:01.670
hasn't

00:03:01.670 --> 00:03:01.680
come.'All

00:03:01.680 --> 00:03:03.830
things continue as they were from

00:03:03.840 --> 00:03:06.070
the beginning of creation without

00:03:06.080 --> 00:03:07.229
missing a

00:03:07.239 --> 00:03:10.149
lick. The Bible says that

00:03:10.149 --> 00:03:10.159
they are

00:03:10.159 --> 00:03:12.630
willingly

00:03:12.640 --> 00:03:15.229
ignorant. They have made up their minds

00:03:15.239 --> 00:03:17.910
that no matter what they

00:03:17.920 --> 00:03:20.670
see, they are going to be untouched by

00:03:20.680 --> 00:03:23.309
it. They have made up their

00:03:23.319 --> 00:03:26.949
minds that no matter what sign is taking

00:03:26.959 --> 00:03:30.509
place in the world on their televisions

00:03:30.519 --> 00:03:31.910
and before their very eyes, they are not

00:03:31.920 --> 00:03:33.309
going to believe. They

00:03:33.309 --> 00:03:33.319
have

00:03:33.319 --> 00:03:37.110
a blindfold

00:03:37.120 --> 00:03:40.350
on; they are willfully ignorant

00:03:40.360 --> 00:03:42.030
of the word of the Lord. The

00:03:42.040 --> 00:03:43.630
heavens were of old and the Earth

00:03:43.640 --> 00:03:46.149
standing out of the water and in the

00:03:46.159 --> 00:03:51.309
water. It says two things:

00:03:51.319 --> 00:03:53.630
'willingly

00:03:53.630 --> 00:03:53.640
ignorant.'Not

00:03:53.640 --> 00:03:57.710
just ignorant, but willingly

00:03:57.720 --> 00:04:00.309
ignorant. They won't let it

00:04:00.319 --> 00:04:04.350
penetrate them, won't think on it, won't

00:04:04.360 --> 00:04:05.869
tell their

00:04:05.879 --> 00:04:07.990
children, and won't discuss it with their

00:04:08.000 --> 00:04:09.630
spouse.

00:04:09.640 --> 00:04:13.229
Pastors won't preach it to their

00:04:13.239 --> 00:04:15.710
congregations; they willingly stick their head

00:04:15.720 --> 00:04:17.710
in the sand or put a blindfold on and

00:04:17.720 --> 00:04:21.069
say, 'No, it's nothing

00:04:21.069 --> 00:04:21.079
important.'I

00:04:21.079 --> 00:04:24.749
saw preachers standing behind the

00:04:24.759 --> 00:04:28.230
pulpit, and they had oil—this

00:04:28.230 --> 00:04:28.240
smooth-looking oil—all

00:04:28.240 --> 00:04:31.270
over their

00:04:31.270 --> 00:04:31.280
mouths,

00:04:31.280 --> 00:04:35.510
and it was dripping from their

00:04:35.520 --> 00:04:39.870
lips. They had roaches and bugs

00:04:39.880 --> 00:04:42.430
crawling in and out of their mouths and

00:04:42.440 --> 00:04:46.310
laying upon their lips. They

00:04:46.320 --> 00:04:48.310
were crawling in their teeth, and the

00:04:48.320 --> 00:04:50.029
bugs were crawling in and out of their

00:04:50.039 --> 00:04:52.510
mouths

00:04:52.520 --> 00:04:53.629
as they

00:04:53.629 --> 00:04:53.639
spoke.

00:04:53.639 --> 00:04:57.909
They had a

00:04:57.909 --> 00:04:57.919
sheen

00:04:57.919 --> 00:05:01.870
in their eyes; their

00:05:01.880 --> 00:05:04.590
motives behind what they were preaching

00:05:04.590 --> 00:05:04.600
were

00:05:04.600 --> 00:05:06.790
all

00:05:06.800 --> 00:05:08.990
selfish

00:05:09.000 --> 00:05:12.550
gain, trying to appease the ears of the

00:05:12.560 --> 00:05:15.710
people. Then I saw the ears of the people,

00:05:15.720 --> 00:05:17.909
and I could see their ears were

00:05:17.919 --> 00:05:21.629
being pacified by all these whispers

00:05:21.639 --> 00:05:23.870
of the things that were happening in the

00:05:23.880 --> 00:05:26.270
spirit.

00:05:26.280 --> 00:05:28.629
'Everything is going to be good; all

00:05:28.639 --> 00:05:30.230
things are going to work for your

00:05:30.240 --> 00:05:31.629
good for those who love the

00:05:31.629 --> 00:05:31.639
Lord.'They

00:05:31.639 --> 00:05:33.430
were speaking the Word, but they

00:05:33.440 --> 00:05:36.110
were not speaking what was on God's

00:05:36.120 --> 00:05:39.110
heart. They were speaking things, but they

00:05:39.120 --> 00:05:42.230
weren't speaking things to make you grow.

00:05:42.240 --> 00:05:44.870
I saw

00:05:44.870 --> 00:05:44.880
those

00:05:44.880 --> 00:05:47.150
bugs coming out of their teeth and

00:05:47.150 --> 00:05:47.160
mouths,

00:05:47.160 --> 00:05:49.590
and the Lord spoke to

00:05:49.600 --> 00:05:52.670
me and said,

00:05:52.680 --> 00:05:54.990
'Brandon, the preachers are not

00:05:55.000 --> 00:05:57.870
teaching the meat of the Word to

00:05:57.880 --> 00:06:00.029
grow My children up

00:06:00.039 --> 00:06:02.749
into adult stature.'And those who are on

00:06:02.759 --> 00:06:05.629
terrorist watch lists are

00:06:05.639 --> 00:06:08.710
crossing into our country now every day,

00:06:08.720 --> 00:06:11.110
many times a

00:06:11.120 --> 00:06:13.550
day. I know that many people coming

00:06:13.560 --> 00:06:16.150
across our borders are desperate for a

00:06:16.160 --> 00:06:18.430
new life and a new start, and I

00:06:18.440 --> 00:06:21.469
understand that. I really do. I feel sorry

00:06:21.479 --> 00:06:22.749
for many of

00:06:22.759 --> 00:06:27.909
them; they are poor, they cannot get healthcare, and

00:06:27.909 --> 00:06:27.919
they dream

00:06:27.919 --> 00:06:30.270
of coming to

00:06:30.280 --> 00:06:31.589
America. I can understand they

00:06:31.589 --> 00:06:31.599
are

00:06:31.599 --> 00:06:34.110
willing to pay any price to get here,

00:06:34.120 --> 00:06:36.270
even if it means coming in illegally, and

00:06:36.280 --> 00:06:38.309
my heart goes out to them. But there are

00:06:38.319 --> 00:06:40.510
many others who have an evil

00:06:40.520 --> 00:06:43.309
intent to destroy our country and

00:06:43.319 --> 00:06:45.270
our way of

00:06:45.280 --> 00:06:48.550
life. I want to show you a scripture; it

00:06:48.550 --> 00:06:48.560
is

00:06:48.560 --> 00:06:51.350
found in Nahum 3:13.

00:06:51.350 --> 00:06:51.360
I am

00:06:51.360 --> 00:06:54.350
going to read it in

00:06:54.360 --> 00:06:55.510
the King James first, and then I am going

00:06:55.520 --> 00:06:57.790
to read it in the NIV and the New Living

00:06:57.800 --> 00:07:00.309
Translation. Here is the King

00:07:00.319 --> 00:07:03.189
James: 'Behold, thy people in the midst of

00:07:03.199 --> 00:07:06.749
thee are women: the gates of thy land

00:07:06.759 --> 00:07:09.510
shall be set wide open unto thine enemies.'In

00:07:09.510 --> 00:07:09.520
Nahum 3:13

00:07:09.520 --> 00:07:13.189
(NIV), it says: 'Look at

00:07:13.199 --> 00:07:16.029
your troops—they are all

00:07:16.039 --> 00:07:18.309
weaklings. The gates of your land are

00:07:18.319 --> 00:07:19.869
wide open to your

00:07:19.869 --> 00:07:19.879
enemies.'But

00:07:19.879 --> 00:07:22.070
this one really gets

00:07:22.070 --> 00:07:22.080
me—the

00:07:22.080 --> 00:07:25.390
New Living Translation: 'Your troops will

00:07:25.400 --> 00:07:28.309
be as weak and helpless as women. The

00:07:28.319 --> 00:07:30.390
gates of your land will be opened wide

00:07:30.400 --> 00:07:31.350
to the enemy.'That

00:07:31.350 --> 00:07:31.360
is

00:07:31.360 --> 00:07:34.110
the southern border. I have

00:07:34.120 --> 00:07:36.869
heard so much talk about the southern

00:07:36.879 --> 00:07:39.510
border and

00:07:39.520 --> 00:07:42.150
how this is

00:07:42.160 --> 00:07:45.149
not happening. This presidential

00:07:45.159 --> 00:07:47.309
candidate said, 'I am going to build a wall

00:07:47.319 --> 00:07:49.510
and we are going to keep them

00:07:49.510 --> 00:07:49.520
out.'Another

00:07:49.520 --> 00:07:51.270
president gets elected and he opens them

00:07:51.280 --> 00:07:54.309
up, and anyone can come. It

00:07:54.309 --> 00:07:54.319
is sickening—it

00:07:54.319 --> 00:07:56.350
is sickening. It is like there is no care

00:07:56.360 --> 00:07:58.990
anymore. We do not care who comes in. We do

00:07:58.990 --> 00:07:59.000
not

00:07:59.000 --> 00:08:00.909
care if they have bombs. We do

00:08:00.909 --> 00:08:00.919
not

00:08:00.919 --> 00:08:02.350
care if a hundred of them come in

00:08:02.350 --> 00:08:02.360
and they

00:08:02.360 --> 00:08:04.070
all have parts to a nuclear

00:08:04.080 --> 00:08:07.110
bomb; they will build it and

00:08:07.120 --> 00:08:09.589
try to have a limited nuclear weapon

00:08:09.599 --> 00:08:11.550
explode somewhere in this country. If

00:08:11.560 --> 00:08:13.510
that happens, I hate to say it, but we

00:08:13.520 --> 00:08:15.749
deserve it because we have

00:08:15.759 --> 00:08:18.110
thrown all caution to the wind. Ladies

00:08:18.120 --> 00:08:20.830
and gentlemen, our country is in great

00:08:20.840 --> 00:08:22.869
peril, and I think it is time

00:08:22.869 --> 00:08:22.879
someone

00:08:22.879 --> 00:08:25.029
stands up and says it. Let me read this

00:08:25.039 --> 00:08:26.589
to you again in the New Living

00:08:26.599 --> 00:08:28.670
Translation: 'Your troops will be as weak

00:08:28.680 --> 00:08:30.309
and helpless as

00:08:30.309 --> 00:08:30.319
women.'In

00:08:30.319 --> 00:08:33.110
other words, the troops will be

00:08:33.120 --> 00:08:34.630
completely

00:08:34.640 --> 00:08:38.190
ineffective. The gates of your land open

00:08:38.200 --> 00:08:41.230
wide to the enemy. Open wide to

00:08:41.230 --> 00:08:41.240
whom?

00:08:41.240 --> 00:08:43.389
To people wanting

00:08:43.399 --> 00:08:45.150
a better life? No, open wide

00:08:45.160 --> 00:08:47.590
to the enemy. You see, what happens when

00:08:47.600 --> 00:08:50.269
you put a blindfold on is the enemy

00:08:50.269 --> 00:08:50.279
is

00:08:50.279 --> 00:08:52.150
coming in, and you do not even care

00:08:52.160 --> 00:08:53.389
anymore.

00:08:53.399 --> 00:08:55.870
Listen: you sow to the wind, you

00:08:55.870 --> 00:08:55.880
will

00:08:55.880 --> 00:08:58.190
reap the

00:08:58.200 --> 00:09:00.190
whirlwind. Now I want to show you this

00:09:00.200 --> 00:09:04.030
scripture in Nahum. This is

00:09:04.040 --> 00:09:06.269
interesting; I think this sums up the

00:09:06.279 --> 00:09:08.110
Biden administration as well as any

00:09:08.120 --> 00:09:09.949
scripture I have ever

00:09:09.959 --> 00:09:13.630
read: 'Behold, I am against thee,'saith the

00:09:13.640 --> 00:09:14.509
Lord of

00:09:14.519 --> 00:09:18.069
hosts; 'I will discover thy skirts upon

00:09:18.069 --> 00:09:18.079
thy

00:09:18.079 --> 00:09:21.310
face; I will show the nations

00:09:21.310 --> 00:09:21.320
thy

00:09:21.320 --> 00:09:24.790
nakedness, and the kingdoms thy

00:09:24.790 --> 00:09:24.800
shame.'In

00:09:24.800 --> 00:09:28.230
the NIV it says: 'I

00:09:28.230 --> 00:09:28.240
am

00:09:28.240 --> 00:09:29.990
against

00:09:29.990 --> 00:09:30.000
you,'declares

00:09:30.000 --> 00:09:31.710
the Lord Almighty. 'I will lift

00:09:31.720 --> 00:09:34.870
your skirts over your face; I will show

00:09:34.880 --> 00:09:36.990
the nations your nakedness and

00:09:37.000 --> 00:09:39.230
the kingdoms your

00:09:39.230 --> 00:09:39.240
shame.'The

00:09:39.240 --> 00:09:41.710
kingdoms of this world are

00:09:41.720 --> 00:09:44.870
seeing how weak our president is and how

00:09:44.880 --> 00:09:47.750
weak his administration

00:09:47.750 --> 00:09:47.760
is—from

00:09:47.760 --> 00:09:49.230
the

00:09:49.240 --> 00:09:51.910
Secretary of Defense to the Secretary of

00:09:51.920 --> 00:09:56.030
State to the president himself. Weak, weak,

00:09:56.040 --> 00:09:59.670
weak, weak. America is in peril,

00:09:59.680 --> 00:10:01.310
and unless something happens pretty

00:10:01.310 --> 00:10:01.320
quickly,

00:10:01.320 --> 00:10:03.470
America is going to be in great

00:10:03.480 --> 00:10:05.190
peril. I

00:10:05.200 --> 00:10:09.509
saw tens of millions of people coming

00:10:09.519 --> 00:10:12.230
from the Mexican border—the southern

00:10:12.230 --> 00:10:12.240
border—trying

00:10:12.240 --> 00:10:15.910
to invade America over the

00:10:15.920 --> 00:10:20.230
next year. But it wasn't all people

00:10:20.240 --> 00:10:22.670
from Mexico. They were

00:10:22.680 --> 00:10:27.470
from all over the world. I literally saw

00:10:27.480 --> 00:10:31.350
millions of people

00:10:31.350 --> 00:10:31.360
coming—millions—so

00:10:31.360 --> 00:10:33.269
much that whenever you're in a

00:10:33.279 --> 00:10:36.230
crowd at a football field or a big

00:10:36.240 --> 00:10:38.269
concert, they're stacked upon

00:10:38.279 --> 00:10:41.430
stacked, all in

00:10:41.440 --> 00:10:45.190
lines. It's like a sea of people

00:10:45.200 --> 00:10:47.470
coming across trying

00:10:47.480 --> 00:10:49.590
to come across the border, but that was

00:10:49.600 --> 00:10:51.470
like all at once, all trying to come

00:10:51.480 --> 00:10:53.389
at once, and there was

00:10:53.399 --> 00:10:54.829
nothing they could do. There were so many

00:10:54.839 --> 00:10:56.629
people seeking

00:10:56.639 --> 00:10:58.550
God for revival because, as well

00:10:58.560 --> 00:11:00.990
as I do now, revival is the only thing

00:11:01.000 --> 00:11:03.509
that will make a difference in America.

00:11:03.519 --> 00:11:06.430
It's the only thing. Revival is the cure

00:11:06.440 --> 00:11:09.629
of all ills. We need the government to be

00:11:09.639 --> 00:11:11.470
on the shoulders of Jesus Christ. That's

00:11:11.480 --> 00:11:15.670
what we need. Come on, somebody help me! I

00:11:15.680 --> 00:11:17.670
said we need the government to be on his

00:11:17.680 --> 00:11:19.870
shoulders. Can you shout,

00:11:19.880 --> 00:11:23.389
